Big Brother Naija season 3 housemate, Cynthia Nwadiora aka Cee-C, seemed to confirm that she contracted COVI-19. On Wednesday, the ‘Double Wahala’ star made reference to the pandemic affecting her this month. In a post on Instagram, she described the virus as an infection “from hell”. ”COVID-19 did a real number on me this January but I wasn’t raised to fold under pressure, I was taught to apply it! “On a more serious note, that virus is definitely from hell, ” she wrote. Cee-C was the 1st runner up in the 2018 of the edition, She is one of the most popular participants that the reality show produced.